Accessor for wellKey

Source: R/AllGenerics.R
getwellKey.Rd

This returns the wellKey, which is a unique identifier generated by idvars in the mapping

getwellKey(sc)

Arguments

sc

An object with a wellKey

Value

integer giving the unique id generated

Examples

data(vbetaFA)
getwellKey(vbetaFA)
